Notes for creating graphs for Maps


trend lines represent time series data
Daily trend for a BFN - this will have trend lines for each BPR with respect to 
y axis : startTime, endTime and duration
x axis : date

stacked bar chart - For showing how diffferent BPRs contribute to the over all duration of a BFN
For example, we had one bad day, so then which BPR contributed the most to that bad day
y axis : %duration for a BPR out of total duration of BFN
x axis : date

Outliers
SLA breaches: 
Which BPR has the highest SLA breaches? Show a bubble chart or tree map

enTime Trend against SLA time

Show trends for end times of different BPRs against their SLAs
https://help.tableau.com/current/pro/desktop/en-us/trendlines_add.htm

Also show the SLA line in the trend chart
https://blogs.perficient.com/2018/06/13/how-to-do-outliers-detection-and-handling-in-tableau/
Add Reference Lines : https://help.tableau.com/current/pro/desktop/en-us/reference_lines.htm
